        <abstract> 
<p>Has received (from CD) the sheets of the second volume [of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>].</p> 
            <p>He fears he has offended CD or someone in England and he begs to know his offence.</p>
            <p>His brother is working at the Red Sea and wishes CD to know that he has evidence for the affinity of ascidians and vertebrates in their nervous systems.</p>
            <p>Plans to go to Paris upon its imminent capitulation to help his sister-in-law.</p>
        </abstract>
